@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title SageStore System Context (Current ERP MVP)

actor Administrator
actor "ERP User" as User
actor "Future API Consumer\n(web/mobile/CLI/integration)" as Consumer

rectangle "SageStore Desktop Client\nQt 6 + MVVM" as Desktop
rectangle "SageStore Server API\nHTTP + Dataset/JSON" as Server
database "SQLite Database" as Db
rectangle "Jenkins CI" as CI

Administrator --> Desktop : users and roles admin tasks
User --> Desktop : login, master data,\npurchasing, sales, inventory,\nanalytics, audit views
Desktop --> Server : /api/users/*\n/api/inventory/*\n/api/management/*\n/api/purchase/*\n/api/sales/*\n/api/logs/*\n/api/analytics/*
Consumer --> Server : same resource contracts
Server --> Db : repositories
CI --> Desktop : build + Qt/unit smoke
CI --> Server : build + unit/contract/integration

note right of Desktop
Desktop-only runtime features:
- settings view
- persisted server defaults
- EN / UA language selection
end note

note bottom of Server
Implemented resources:
- users/login
- users/users
- users/roles
- inventory/product-types
- inventory/stocks
- inventory/supplier-products
- management/contacts
- management/suppliers
- management/employees
- purchase/orders
- purchase/order-records
- purchase/receipts
- sales/orders
- sales/order-records
- logs/entries
- analytics/sales
- analytics/inventory
end note

@enduml
